[[File:CZcommunicationsdroid-NEGTD.png|thumb|right|220px|A CZ-series droid]]
A '''communications droid''', also called '''comms droid''', was a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] that specialized in communications. They were expensive droid that was capable of sending and receiving communications. It boasted the ability to float, and had a [[Chronometer/Legends|chronometer]] built into it. Examples of such droids included the [[ET-74 communications droid]] and the [[CZ-series secretary/comm droid|CZ-series communications/business droid]]. Some owners of [[RX-series pilot droid/Legends|RX-Series pilot droids]] modified them to serve as communications droids.

[[Soergg Vosadii Bezhin|Soerrgg]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] owned several commdroids for his personal use.

